$ certutil.exe

{ -encode / -decode #certutil-encode-decode

  The two command line options `-encode` and `-decode` provide a possibilty to encode or decode a file in/from → development/Base64
  when only native tools of → Windows can be usedr:
code {
C:\> certutil -encode file.txt file.64
C:\> certutil -decode file.64  file.txt
code }

}
